{"tid":1611862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"10月5號和你Shop全民支持與港人同行良心店","createTime":"2019-10-02T05:24:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T17:36:56.000Z","uid":6435,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2e6129f1a00b7ccb41af7603194543d0921d93ae","tid":1611862,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:24:11.000Z","msg":"罷買罷食唔係一時三刻做到<br />\n要養成一個擺脫支資舖頭同服務嘅習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10月5號就嚟第一波和你Shop行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一齊身體力行用行動同埋銀兩支持各大小與港人同行嘅良心舖頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一齊買到佢無貨 食到佢清倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n與此同時可以同步進行就係即時去取消所有支資服務 例如支那銀號 支那移動 唔好再比錢佢地搵<br />\n<br />\n部分賣港商號就齋坐唔消費<br />\n<br />\n總之用行動養成習慣 一步一步擺脫支那控制<br />\n由生活習慣拎返香港人嘅自主權<br />\n將所有支那野踢出香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d98c59e0c1408558e113c7d001f7c9d526489116","tid":1611862,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:34:43.000Z","msg":"Pish 全民消費日"},{"pid":"67221af019db49d2a50ec1104a43085634e28c06","tid":1611862,"uid":205937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:35:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"27c824eedda502e1482227984adb432b6c48014f","tid":1611862,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:40:17.000Z","msg":"人地拎副身家嚟撐香港人<br />\n香港人同我買到無貨食到清倉"},{"pid":"e6fc5010b38b27d219e7ce934f0452381fdc8476","tid":1611862,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:40:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0cb1f672e25e32f86410cf0b5bce510764ce786f","tid":1611862,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:43:08.000Z","msg":"既然未有活動就一於一家大細扶老攜幼出嚟消費"},{"pid":"0d28cbe5e041a73a67071f57f87986c796d9d3d8","tid":1611862,"uid":2